<h5>Approval History Component</h5>
<p>Displays a chronological timeline of approval actions for a specific approval request.</p>

<h6>Options:</h6>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Request ID</strong> - Datasource binding for the approval request ID whose history should be displayed.</li>
    <li><strong>History Records</strong> - Optional pre-loaded history records datasource.</li>
    <li><strong>Display Mode</strong> - Choose between "compact" or "detailed" timeline view.</li>
    <li><strong>Max Records</strong> - Maximum number of history entries to show (0 for unlimited).</li>
    <li><strong>Show Timestamps</strong> - Toggle visibility of date/time on each history entry.</li>
    <li><strong>Show Comments</strong> - Toggle visibility of approval comments.</li>
    <li><strong>Show User Avatars</strong> - Toggle visibility of user profile images.</li>
    <li><strong>CSS Class</strong> - Additional CSS classes to apply to the component.</li>
    <li><strong>Empty State Text</strong> - Custom message when no history records are found.</li>
</ul>

<h6>Action Types Displayed:</h6>
<ul>
    <li><span class="badge badge-success">Approve</span> - Request was approved</li>
    <li><span class="badge badge-danger">Reject</span> - Request was rejected</li>
    <li><span class="badge badge-info">Delegate</span> - Request was delegated to another approver</li>
    <li><span class="badge badge-warning">Escalate</span> - Request was escalated</li>
    <li><span class="badge badge-secondary">Comment</span> - A comment was added</li>
    <li><span class="badge badge-primary">Submit</span> - Request was submitted for approval</li>
</ul>

